    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a pot with a lid with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once melted, add the <strong>white long grain rice </strong>with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until toasted</p><p>Tip: Watch it like a hawk to make sure it doesn't burn!</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
