      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once toasted, add the <strong>coriander paste</strong> with 225ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[450ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> to the rice and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Once cooked, remove from the heat and keep covered until serving – this is your <strong>green rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
