    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the rice is cooking, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> marinated chicken</strong> and cook for 8-9 min on each side or until cooked through and slightly charred (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>chipotle chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
