    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>chipotle chicken</strong> with the <strong>green rice</strong> and <strong>elote corn</strong> to the side</p><p>Squeeze the juice of a <strong>lime wedge</strong> over the green rice</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong> and a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
